Document: RenderSceneBuffersConfiguration
Path: godot/classes/class_renderscenebuffersconfiguration.rst
Summary: Configuration for render scene buffers.

Inherits: Resource < RefCounted < Object

This class holds configuration for render scene buffers. It allows for fine-grained control over how the scene is rendered, including buffer formats, resolutions, and other rendering-related settings. This is useful for advanced rendering techniques and custom render pipelines.
